<h2>Related: lead capture (not pricing)</h2>
<p><code>POST /api/ghl/lead</code> forwards to <code>GHL_LEAD_WEBHOOK_URL</code> — separate from the pricing checkout flow. See <code>src/app/api/ghl/lead/route.ts</code> and <code>README.md</code>.</p></body></html>